#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. Life Span "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Paṭhamaāyusutta "
msgstr "9. Life Span (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn4.9:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn4.9:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

msgctxt "sn4.9:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "sn4.9:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.9:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "sn4.9:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn4.9:2.1"
msgid "“Appamidaṃ, bhikkhave, manussānaṃ āyu. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the life span of humans is short. "

msgctxt "sn4.9:2.2"
msgid "Gamanīyo samparāyo, kattabbaṃ kusalaṃ, caritabbaṃ brahmacariyaṃ. "
msgstr "You must go to the next life. So you should do what is skillful, you should practice the spiritual life. "

msgctxt "sn4.9:2.3"
msgid "Natthi jātassa amaraṇaṃ. "
msgstr "No-one born is immortal. "

msgctxt "sn4.9:2.4"
msgid "Yo, bhikkhave, ciraṃ jīvati, so vassasataṃ appaṃ vā bhiyyo”ti. "
msgstr "A long life is a hundred years or a little more.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn4.9:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn4.9:4.1"
msgid "“Dīghamāyu manussānaṃ, "
msgstr "“The life of humans is long! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.9:4.2"
msgid "na naṃ hīḷe suporiso; "
msgstr "A good person wouldn’t scorn it. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.9:4.3"
msgid "Careyya khīramattova, "
msgstr "Live like a suckling babe, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.9:4.4"
msgid "natthi maccussa āgamo”ti. "
msgstr "for Death has not come for you.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.242, sc5
msgctxt "sn4.9:5.1"
msgid "“Appamāyu manussānaṃ, "
msgstr "“The life of humans is short, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.9:5.2"
msgid "hīḷeyya naṃ suporiso; "
msgstr "and a good person scorns it. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.9:5.3"
msgid "Careyyādittasīsova, "
msgstr "They should live as though their head was on fire, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.9:5.4"
msgid "natthi maccussa nāgamo”ti. "
msgstr "for Death comes for everyone.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn4.9:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro … pe … tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra … vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
